[ Presentation ]
----------------
VirtualBattle is a battle simulator based on finite state machines. It is 
programmed in C++ with SDL and OpenGL.

[ Compiling ]
-------------
Once the archive unzipped, go into the root directory and type `make'.

[ Running ]
-----------
Run the program by typing `./main'.

[ Documentation ]
-----------------
For any extra information, please read the documentation. You can generate it 
by typing `make doc'.
